INSERT INTO `call_strategies` (`strategy_id`, `industry_id`, `call_strategy`) VALUES
(2, 1, '<p><strong>Call Pitch Structure For Construction Industry&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>30-Seconds Pitch Structure (4 Key Steps)</strong></p><p><strong>Intro:</strong><br>Hi, I won’t take much of your time—can I quickly share something that’s helping construction teams reduce payroll errors and improve on-site tracking?</p><p><strong>1. Hook (Problem):</strong><br>Manual attendance methods like paper logs or registers often lead to buddy punching, fake check-ins, and payroll mismatches across sites.</p><p><strong>2. Solution:</strong><br>We offer a GPS-based geo-attendance system with facial recognition that captures accurate check-ins and check-outs for every worker on-site.</p><p><strong>3. Value Proposition:</strong><br>It’s helping construction companies reduce time fraud by up to 25% and significantly improve workforce accountability.</p><p><strong>4. Call to Action:</strong><br>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute demo next week to see how it could fit into your site operations?</p><h3><br><strong>60–90 Seconds Pitch Structure&nbsp;</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Intro (One-liner):</strong><br>Hi, I’ll be quick—would it be okay if I take just over a minute to share how we’re helping construction teams track worker attendance more accurately and reduce payroll errors using geo-attendance?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>On large construction sites, it’s tough to know exactly who’s on-site and when. Paper-based attendance or manual logs often lead to buddy punching, ghost workers, and payroll mismatches—costing time and money.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) – 15–20 seconds</strong></p><p>We offer a mobile-based geo-attendance system that uses GPS and facial recognition to log real-time check-ins and check-outs. Site managers and HR teams can instantly see who’s on-site, track shift hours, and avoid manual errors across multiple locations.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 15–20 seconds</strong></p><p>Construction firms using our solution have seen up to 30% fewer payroll disputes, eliminated fake attendance entries, and simplified wage processing. It’s especially useful for subcontractor management and shift-based labor visibility.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute walkthrough? I can show how it fits directly into your existing attendance and payroll workflow.</p>'),
(5, 7, '<p><strong>30-Second Call Pitch For Healthcare Services:</strong></p><p><strong>Introduction[You]:</strong></p><p>Hi [Prospect\'s Name], this is [Your Name] from Geo Attendance. Is this a right time for quick call for 30 second?&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 5–7 seconds</strong></p><p>“Many healthcare teams struggle to verify if field staff are actually reaching patients on time—leading to missed visits, compliance risks, and patient dissatisfaction.”</p><p><strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) – 7–10 seconds</strong></p><p>“Our Geo Attendance system uses GPS check-ins to confirm staff are at the right location, on time—giving you real-time visibility, accurate logs, and better patient care tracking.”</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 7–10 seconds</strong></p><p>“Healthcare providers using our system have cut no-show rates by up to 30%, improved staff accountability, and saved hours in manual reporting every week.”</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) – 5 seconds</strong></p><p>“Let’s schedule a quick demo to show you how it works in real-time—what time works best for you?”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>60-Second Call Pitch For Healthcare Services:</strong></p><p><strong>Introduction[You]:</strong></p><p>Hi [Prospect\'s Name], this is [Your Name] from Geo Attendance. Is this a right time for quick call for 1minute?&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>“In healthcare, especially with home visits and field staff, it’s hard to track if workers are reaching patients on time. Manual attendance is unreliable, and missed visits can lead to compliance issues, patient dissatisfaction, and wasted resources.”</p><p><strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) -15-20seconds</strong></p><p>“Our Geo Attendance solution lets healthcare staff check in and out at patient locations using GPS-enabled mobile devices. This gives managers real-time visibility into field activity, verifies visits, ensures timely care delivery, and replaces unreliable paper-based tracking with accurate digital records.”</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 15-20 seconds</strong></p><p>“By using our Geo Attendance solution, healthcare providers have improved field staff accountability, reduced missed or falsified visits, and saved hours each week on manual reporting. This leads to better patient outcomes, increased operational efficiency, and stronger compliance with healthcare standards.”</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) –10-15 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Transform your healthcare operations with real-time geo-attendance tracking. Improve staff accountability, ensure timely care, and optimize resource allocation. Start today to provide better service and reduce operational costs.\"-THANK YOU.</p>'),
(6, 8, '<p><strong>Call Pitch Structure For Construction Industry&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>30-Seconds Pitch Structure (4 Key Steps)</strong></p><p><strong>Intro:</strong><br>Hi, I won’t take much of your time—can I quickly share something that’s helping construction teams reduce payroll errors and improve on-site tracking?</p><p><strong>1. Hook (Problem):</strong><br>Manual attendance methods like paper logs or registers often lead to buddy punching, fake check-ins, and payroll mismatches across sites.</p><p><strong>2. Solution:</strong><br>We offer a GPS-based geo-attendance system with facial recognition that captures accurate check-ins and check-outs for every worker on-site.</p><p><strong>3. Value Proposition:</strong><br>It’s helping construction companies reduce time fraud by up to 25% and significantly improve workforce accountability.</p><p><strong>4. Call to Action:</strong><br>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute demo next week to see how it could fit into your site operations?</p><h3><br><strong>60–90 Seconds Pitch Structure&nbsp;</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Intro (One-liner):</strong><br>Hi, I’ll be quick—would it be okay if I take just over a minute to share how we’re helping construction teams track worker attendance more accurately and reduce payroll errors using geo-attendance?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>On large construction sites, it’s tough to know exactly who’s on-site and when. Paper-based attendance or manual logs often lead to buddy punching, ghost workers, and payroll mismatches—costing time and money.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) – 15–20 seconds</strong></p><p>We offer a mobile-based geo-attendance system that uses GPS and facial recognition to log real-time check-ins and check-outs. Site managers and HR teams can instantly see who’s on-site, track shift hours, and avoid manual errors across multiple locations.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 15–20 seconds</strong></p><p>Construction firms using our solution have seen up to 30% fewer payroll disputes, eliminated fake attendance entries, and simplified wage processing. It’s especially useful for subcontractor management and shift-based labor visibility.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute walkthrough? I can show how it fits directly into your existing attendance and payroll workflow.</p>'),
(7, 9, '<p><strong>30-Second Call Pitch For Logistics:</strong></p><p><strong>Introduction[You]:</strong></p><p>Hi [Prospect\'s Name], this is [Your Name] from Geo Attendance. Is this a right time for quick call for 30 second?&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 5–7 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Every minute of delay in logistics costs money—yet inefficiencies, poor tracking, and outdated systems are still the norm.\"</p><p><strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) – 7–10 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Our geo-attendance system tracks workforce location in real-time, ensuring accountability, streamlining dispatch, and cutting operational delays.\"</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 7–10 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Boost delivery efficiency by up to 30%, reduce fuel costs, and gain complete visibility of your field teams—all through smart geo-attendance tracking.\"</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) – 5 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Streamline your operations today—start using geo-attendance to track, optimize, and boost your logistics efficiency.\"-THANK YOU.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>60-Second Call Pitch For Logistics:</strong></p><p><strong>Introduction[You]:</strong></p><p>Hi [Prospect\'s Name], this is [Your Name] from Geo Attendance. Is this a right time for quick call for 1minute?&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 10-15 seconds</strong></p><p>\"In logistics, every delay, miscommunication, or missed check-in adds up—leading to lost time, higher costs, and unhappy customers. Yet, many operations still rely on outdated tracking and manual attendance.</p><p>\"<strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) –15-20 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Our geo-attendance solution enables logistics companies to track field staff in real-time, automate attendance based on location, and optimize routes and dispatching. This not only reduces manual errors and delays but also ensures greater accountability, faster deliveries, and improved resource utilization.\"</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 15-20seconds</strong></p><p>\"With our geo-attendance solution, logistics teams gain real-time visibility of on-ground staff, leading to faster deliveries, reduced idle time, and improved route efficiency. Companies have seen up to 30% better resource utilization and a significant drop in delivery delays.\"</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) – 10-15 seconds</strong></p><p>\"Ready to take control of your field operations? Schedule a demo today and see how our geo-attendance system can boost efficiency, cut costs, and give you real-time visibility—right from your dashboard.\"-THANK YOU.</p>'),
(8, 10, '<p><strong>Facility Management Sector</strong></p><p><strong>Cold Call Script — 30 seconds</strong></p><p><strong>Opening (0-10 seconds)</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong><br><i>\"Hi, I’m Pallavi from GeoAttendance. Do you have a quick minute to talk?\"</i></p><p><strong>If yes, continue. If no — thank them and hang up.</strong></p><p><strong>Initial Question (10-20 seconds)</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong><br><i>\"Thank you! Just curious — how are you currently tracking attendance for your staff across different sites or remote locations?\"</i></p><p><i><strong>(Let them answer.)</strong></i></p><p><strong>If they say “not interested” or “we already have an attendance app” and don’t seem open:</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi (at around 25-30 seconds):</strong><br>\"No problem at all — thank you so much for your time today. Wishing you a great day ahead!\"</p><p><i><strong>(End call.)</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Cold Call Script — 60-90 seconds</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Hi, I’m Pallavi from GeoAttendance. Do you have a quick minute?\"</p><p><strong>Facility Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Yeah, go ahead.\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Thanks! Just wanted to ask—how do you currently track attendance for your ground teams? Like cleaners, security staff, or maintenance personnel working across different buildings?\"</p><p><strong>Facility Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Mostly through manual registers or supervisor reports. We collect everything at the end of the day.\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Got it—that’s what a lot of teams do. But we’ve seen that manual methods often lead to missed entries, buddy punching, or even disputes during payroll.\"</p><p><strong>Facility Manager</strong>:</p><p>\"Yeah, it’s not perfect. Especially when staff rotate between locations.\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Exactly. That’s where GeoAttendance helps. It’s a mobile app where staff can check in and out using their phones, and we use GPS to verify their location. So, no more paper logs or unreliable reporting.\"</p><p><strong>Facility Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Interesting. But what if there’s no internet at a site?\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Good question—it works offline too. Data gets stored locally and syncs when the phone reconnects. Plus, you get real-time dashboards and reports, which help streamline payroll and ensure transparency across locations.\"</p><p><strong>Facility Manager:</strong></p><p>\"That could really help us.\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"I’d love to send you a short demo—it takes just 10 minutes. Would WhatsApp or email be better for you?\"</p>'),
(9, 11, '<h3><strong>30-Second Call Script – Computer &amp; Office Equipment Sales</strong></h3><p><strong>Caller (You):</strong><br>Hi [Official Name], this is [Your Name] from <strong>BranchTrack</strong>. Did I catch you at a decent time?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>What’s this about?</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>I’ll keep it quick — we help computer and office equipment businesses streamline field staff tracking and attendance with GPS-enabled mobile check-ins.<br>Out of curiosity — are your sales reps still reporting attendance manually or through spreadsheets?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Yeah, mostly manual or WhatsApp updates.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Got it. Our app lets them check in from anywhere with GPS and a selfie — no hardware needed.<br>Would you be open to a quick 10-minute demo tomorrow morning?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Sure, that sounds fine.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Perfect — I’ll send over a calendar invite. Thanks, [Official Name]!</p><h3><strong>60-Second Call Script – Computer &amp; Office Equipment Sales</strong></h3><p><strong>Caller (You):</strong><br>Hi [Official Name], this is [Your Name] from <strong>BranchTrack</strong>. Is this a good time for a quick chat?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Depends — what’s this about?</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Absolutely, I’ll be brief. We work with computer and office equipment companies to digitize field staff operations — especially attendance, location tracking, and accountability.</p><p>Are you currently using any tools for monitoring your field sales teams, or is it still done manually?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>It’s mostly manual — calls, WhatsApp messages, and Excel tracking.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>That\'s very common. Branch Track allows your team to check in from the field using a mobile app — GPS-tagged with a selfie, no biometric devices required.<br>It even works offline and syncs later — ideal for reps visiting client sites in low-network areas.</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>That could actually help. We often struggle to track actual field visits.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Exactly. A lot of our clients start with a 2-branch pilot to cut admin work and boost visibility.<br>Would a short 10-minute demo tomorrow at 10 AM work for you?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Yes, that’s fine.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Great! I’ll send the invite. Appreciate your time, [Official Name].</p>'),
(10, 12, '<p><strong>Telecommunication Sector</strong></p><p><strong>Cold Call Script — 30 seconds</strong></p><p><strong>Opening (0-10 seconds)</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong><br><i>\"Hi, I’m Pallavi from GeoAttendance. Do you have a quick minute to talk?\"</i></p><p><strong>If yes, continue. If no — thank them and hang up.</strong></p><p><strong>Initial Question (10-20 seconds)</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong><br><i>\"Thank you! Just curious — how are you currently tracking attendance for your staff across different sites or remote locations?\"</i></p><p><i><strong>(Let them answer.)</strong></i></p><p><strong>If they say “not interested” or “we already have an attendance app” and don’t seem open:</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi (at around 25-30 seconds):</strong><br>\"No problem at all — thank you so much for your time today. Wishing you a great day ahead!\"</p><p><i><strong>(End call.)</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Cold Call Script — 60-90 seconds</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Hi, I’m Pallavi from GeoAttendance. Do you have a minute to talk?\"</p><p><strong>Telecom Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Yeah, sure. What is it about?\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Thanks! Quick question—how are you currently tracking attendance for your field technicians or engineers working at tower sites?\"</p><p><strong>Telecom Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Mostly through WhatsApp messages or supervisor check-ins. Sometimes, we collect reports at the&nbsp;<strong>end of the day.\"</strong></p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Right—many telecom teams do that, but it can lead to a lot of confusion. We\'ve seen issues like time theft, inaccurate records, and delays in payroll and reporting.\"</p><p><strong>Telecom Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Exactly. We do run into those—especially when teams are working remotely.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"That’s exactly what we help with. GeoAttendance is a mobile GPS-based app. Field staff check in and out using their phones, and their location is automatically captured—even in remote areas. It works offline too, so data syncs once the device reconnects.\"</p><p><strong>Telecom Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Hmm, that sounds useful. Does it also generate reports?\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi:</strong></p><p>\"Yes—it provides real-time dashboards and auto-generated reports for attendance, location, and hours worked. It helps save time, reduce payroll errors, and improve accountability.\"</p><p><strong>Telecom Manager:</strong></p><p>\"Interesting. Can you send me some details?\"</p><p><strong>Pallavi</strong>:</p><p>\"Absolutely! I can send you a short demo—just 10 minutes. Would WhatsApp or email be easier for you?\"</p>'),
(11, 13, '<p><strong>30-Second Play Role (FMCG – Field Sales Team Tracking)</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Caller (You):</strong><br>Hi [Official Name], this is [Your Name] from GeoAttendance. Is this a good time for a quick chat?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Depends—what’s this about?</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>I completely understand. I\'ll keep this brief. We assist FMCG companies in streamlining field staff attendance through GPS-based mobile check-ins. Just to understand better—does your team currently use manual methods like paper logs or WhatsApp for attendance tracking?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Yes, mostly manual methods.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>That\'s quite common. Our solution is designed to enhance such setups. Field staff can check in using a selfie and GPS via their smartphones, even in offline mode. This ensures accurate and real-time attendance tracking, which is crucial for FMCG operations where timely deliveries and market visits are essential.</p><p>Would you be open to a short 10-minute demo tomorrow morning to see how this could benefit your team?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Sure, maybe 10 AM?</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Perfect. I\'ll send over a calendar invite with the demo link. Looking forward to connecting then. Thanks, [Official Name].</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>---</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>60-Second Play Role (FMCG)</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>aller (You):</strong><br>Hi [Official Name], this is [Your Name] from GeoAttendance. Is this a good time for a quick chat?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Depends—what’s this about?</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>I’ll be brief — we assist FMCG companies in streamlining field staff attendance using mobile GPS check-ins. Are you currently using a digital solution, or is attendance still manual for your field teams?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Still manual — usually WhatsApp or paper sheets.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Understood — that\'s quite common. Our app simplifies this by enabling GPS and selfie-based check-ins via mobile devices. It even functions offline, ensuring accurate attendance tracking in areas with poor connectivity.</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>That’s definitely a challenge for us.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Exactly — offline check-ins sync automatically once back online. You can implement GeoAttendance selectively, focusing on regions or teams where oversight is most needed.</p><p>Would you be open to a quick 10-minute demo tomorrow at 10 AM?</p><p><strong>Official:</strong><br>Sure, let’s do that.</p><p><strong>You:</strong><br>Perfect! I’ll send the invite and link shortly. Appreciate your time, [Official Name]!</p><p>&nbsp;</p>'),
(12, 14, '<p><strong>Call Pitch Structure For Pharmaceutical Industry</strong><br><br><strong>30-Seconds Pitch Structure (4 Key Steps)</strong></p><p><strong>Intro:</strong><br>Hi, can I take just half a minute to show how we’re helping pharma facilities streamline attendance tracking and fix payroll errors?</p><p><strong>1. Hook (Problem):</strong><br>Manual logs and swipe cards often result in inaccurate attendance, buddy punching, and delays in salary processing.</p><p><strong>2. Solution:</strong><br>Our geo-attendance system uses facial recognition and GPS to log employee presence in real-time—no manual intervention required.</p><p><strong>3. Value Proposition:</strong><br>Pharma clients have seen up to 30% fewer payroll issues and better shift-wise visibility across departments and contract staff.</p><p><strong>4. Call to Action:</strong><br>Would a 15-minute demo work for you sometime next week? I’d love to walk you through how it fits into your existing setup.</p><p><br><br><strong>60–90 Seconds Pitch Structure</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Intro (One-liner):</strong><br>Hi, I know you\'re tight on time—can I take just over a minute to share how we\'re helping pharma companies improve attendance accuracy and reduce payroll errors through geo-attendance tracking?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Hook (Problem Statement) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>In pharma facilities, managing shifts across production, packaging, and quality teams is complex. Relying on manual attendance logs or swipe cards often leads to errors, time fraud, buddy punching, and inconsistent payroll—especially in high-volume operations.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Solution (What Your Product Does) – 15–20 seconds</strong></p><p>Our geo-attendance system uses GPS and facial recognition to track employee check-ins and check-outs with precision—right from their mobile devices or designated zones within the plant. It gives HR and operations full visibility on who’s working, where, and for how long.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Value Proposition (Impact &amp; Results) – 15–20 seconds</strong></p><p>Pharma companies using our platform have reduced payroll errors by over 30%, eliminated time theft, and streamlined shift management—especially in 24x7 facilities. It’s helped HR teams process salaries faster and ensured accurate workforce utilization without manual cross-checks.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Call to Action (Next Step) – 10–15 seconds</strong></p><p>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute demo next week? I’d love to show you how this can fit into your current setup and make workforce tracking a lot simpler and more accurate.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>');

