(27, 'Attendance in Computer & Office Equipment Sales', 11, '<h3>Our robust workforce management offers</h3><ul><li>Managing Multi-Location Attendance</li><li>Geotagging attendance with a Selfie</li><li>Real-time Employee tracking</li><li>Task Management with Dashboards</li><li>Automated Timesheets &amp; Payroll</li></ul>', '<ul><li><strong>Inefficient Time Tracking</strong></li></ul><p>Manual attendance tracking can be time-consuming and error-prone, resulting in inaccurate data and potential payroll discrepancies.</p><ul><li><strong>Limited Transparency</strong></li></ul><p>Lack of real-time visibility into the attendance and location of your sales team can hinder effective management and decision-making.</p><ul><li><strong>Compliance Issues</strong></li></ul><p>Adhering to labor laws and company policies without an automated system can be challenging and increase the risk of non-compliance.</p><ul><li><strong>Employee Accountability</strong></li></ul><p>Without a robust system, ensuring accountability and tracking the productivity of your remote sales team can be difficult.</p>', '<ul><li><strong>Increased Efficiency</strong></li></ul><p>Save valuable time and resources by automating attendance and performance tracking processes.</p><ul><li><strong>Improved Accuracy</strong></li></ul><p>Ensure precise attendance data and payroll calculations, reducing errors and discrepancies.</p><ul><li><strong>Better Decision-Making</strong></li></ul><p>Leverage real-time insights to make informed decisions and optimize your sales operations.</p><ul><li><strong>Enhanced Compliance</strong></li></ul><p>Stay compliant with labor laws and company policies effortlessly, minimizing legal risks.</p><ul><li><strong>Boosted Productivity</strong></li></ul><p>Monitor and improve your sales team\'s performance and accountability, leading to increased sales and revenue.</p>'),
